# terraform init 
######################################
1. use repo to setup vim for terraform https://github.com/hashivim/vim-terraform/blob/master/.editorconfig
2.resource "<PROVIDER>_<TYPE>" "<NAME>" {
    [CONFIG ...]
  } #  TF general syntax 
3. terraform init # Dowloads a providers code/plugin to your project 
4. The <<-EOF and EOF are Terraformâ€™s heredoc syntax
5. Remove all spaces hwen defining user_data
6. <PROVIDER>_<TYPE>.<NAME>.<ATTRIBUTE> # Tf refference expresion e.g  ${aws_security_group.example_sg.id} aka implicit dependency 
7. https://docs.aws.amazon.com/IAM/latest/UserGuide/best-practices.html # secure aws resources
8. https://gist.github.com/willurd/5720255 # list of oneliner webserver
9. https://www.airpair.com/aws/posts/building-a-scalable-web-app-on-amazon-web-services-p1 # More aws best practises




